    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We present Alpha-BET, a structure-guided strategy leveraging AlphaFold to identify optimal ALFA-tag insertion sites for minimally disruptive labeling of viral glycoproteins with high-affinity nanobodies. Applied to HIV-1 Env, SARS-CoV-2 S, and NiV G, Alpha-BET preserves structural integrity and function. For HIV-1 Env, we demonstrate super-resolution DNA-PAINT MINFLUX 3D imaging enabled by tag insertion, showcasing its power for visualizing native trimers in single virions and potential for broader applications in virus research.</jats:p>",
